name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Petitioner, v. Michael MASTROMARINO, Respondent

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Petitioner, v. Michael MASTROMARINO, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 17th day of December, 2007, the Commonwealth’s Emergency Petitions filed December 13, 2007, are DENIED and the single-Justice Order entered December 14, 2007, extending the stay is VACATED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Petitioner, v. Michael MASTROMARINO, Respondent.
